reviewText: This is a fine concert, I can't add anything that all the other reviews have stated so nicely...EXCEPT...the import version of this concert includes a 20 minute live Crusaders show from the late 70's, and features (then) Crusaders guitarist Larry Carlton, which includes a live version of "Spiral".  Great stuff!  There is very little live stuff on Carlton from that period and the Crusaders sound much more inspired in that footage, I must say!
summary: Get the Japanese version with bonus Larry Carlton footage!
